    {
      "instruction": "<p>Top, tail, peel and dice your <strong>carrot[s]</strong> finely</p><p>Drain your<strong> tofu </strong>and pat it dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Cut the <strong>drained</strong> <strong>tofu</strong> into 6 strips per person</p>",
