    {
      "instruction": "<p>Whilst the rice is cooking, add the <strong>tofu strips</strong> to a bowl with <strong>half</strong> of your <strong>soy sauce</strong> (you'll use the rest later!) and your <strong>cornflour</strong> and give everything a good mix up until fully coated</p><p>Boil half a kettle</p>",
