      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick with a matching lid) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>coated tofu strips</strong> and cook for 3 min on each side or until<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span>browned</p><p>While the tofu is browning, combine your <strong>agave</strong>, <strong>chilli relish</strong> and 30ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[45ml] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[60ml]</span> <strong>cold water </strong>– this is your <strong>sweet chilli sauce</strong></p>",
