    {
      "instruction": "<p>Peel and finely slice (don't chop!) your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Once the tofu has browned, turn the heat down to medium-low and add the<strong> sliced garlic </strong>and cook for 1 min or until slightly softened</p><p>Add the <strong>sweet chilli sauce </strong>to the pan and cook for a further 5 min or until the sauce has thickened</p>",
