    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>blanched peas</strong> to a colander and pour <strong>boiled water</strong> all over them to refresh them</p><p>Once the rice is cooked, add the<strong> refreshed peas</strong>, <strong>black sesame seeds</strong> and <strong>remaining soy sauce</strong> and mix everything together – this is your <strong>veg-packed rice</strong></p>",
